 2010-07392010-06-10,  ,  ,  AAFC, 
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - Ontario Tornado Assistance Initiative
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide assistance through the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program under the AgriRecovery Framework to apple and other tree fruit producers in the Georgian Bay region of Ontario whose orchards were destroyed by a tornado through a contribution under the federal component of the 2010 ONTARIO TORNADO ASSISTANCE INITIATIVE.
